prompts.prompt: I need code to evaluate a test of Python proficiency done by a candidate. The test involved creating a Spring Boot project with various features including REST API development, database integration, JWT authentication, integration with an external API, email service, automated testing, messaging with RabbitMQ, caching with Redis, and deployment with monitoring. The test is available at https://github.com/PetrusJCMSilva/Desafio-1. Please provide a script or tool to analyze and evaluate the code quality, architectural decisions, and implementation of the specified features in this GitHub repository.
